snippet: David Rudisha, the world and Olympic champion, cruised to victory in the 800 meters at the season-opening Diamond League meet in Doha, Qatar.
abstract: Olympic champion runner David Rudisha wins 800 meters at season-opening Diamond League meet in Doha, Qatar; other track and field news noted.
lead_paragraph: David Rudisha, the world and Olympic champion, cruised to victory in the 800 meters at the season-opening Diamond League meet in Doha, Qatar.
